# Skills Platform Rule

This repository is a Skills-driven AI platform.

- Do not hide AI prompts, personas, or business AI behavior in source code.
- Add or update reusable Skills under `skills/` for new AI capabilities.
- Source code may route, validate, log, cache, and call providers.
- Every AI output must be schema validated and have fallback behavior.
- Prefer reusing or composing existing Skills before creating new ones.
